        <div class="blog-grid">
            <!-- Insight 1: Verified Data -->
            <div class="blog-card" style="border-left: 4px solid #1e3c72;">
                <h3>Why African Data Revolution Must be <span style="color: #4a7ab5;">Verified</span></h3>
                <p>AI is only as good as the data it learns from. And right now, the world's most important data is the least verified.</p>
                <a href="insight-verified.html" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Insight 2: Last Mile -->
            <div class="blog-card" style="border-left: 4px solid #4a7ab5;">
                <h3>The <span style="color: #4a7ab5;">Last Mile</span> of Intelligence</h3>
