    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- FAQ - SHORTENED                                              -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <section id="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Quick answers to common questions about working with us.</p>

            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item active">
                    <h4>What types of research do you handle? <span class="toggle">−</span></h4>
                    <p>We handle market research, data analysis, M&E for NGOs, medical and pharmaceutical research, AI
                        fact-checking, and professional training. Our team has deep expertise across healthcare,
                        agriculture, finance, and international development.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>Who do you work with? <span class="toggle">+</span></h4>
                    <p>We work with NGOs, businesses, government agencies, academic institutions, and development
                        partners across Kenya and internationally. Recent partners include UNICEF and Kenya's Ministry
                        of Health.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>How long does a typical project take? <span class="toggle">+</span></h4>
                    <p>Timelines vary depending on scope. A market research study might take 2–4 weeks, while a
                        comprehensive M&E evaluation could take 3–6 months. We provide a clear timeline in our proposal
                        before we start.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>How do you ensure data quality and confidentiality? <span class="toggle">+</span></h4>
                    <p>We follow rigorous quality assurance protocols at every stage. Our team is GCP certified, and we
                        have a proven track record of reducing data errors by over 30%. All client data is handled with
                        the highest level of confidentiality.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>What does the process look like?<span class="toggle">+</span></h4>
                    <p>We follow a transparent 5-step process: Consult Define (understand your needs),
                        Proposal Plan (scope and timeline), Collect
                        Verify (field research and data collection), Analyze Interpret
                        (rigorous analysis), and Report Recommend (clear, actionable insights).</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- CONTACT                                                      -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <section id="contact" class="section-alt">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Get In Touch</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Whether you're solving a research challenge, exploring a partnership, or ready to invest in Africa's data future — we're here to listen. Start with a conversation.</p>
            <div class="contact-grid">
                <div class="contact-info-box">
                    <h3>Contact Details</h3>
                    <div class="detail">
                        <span class="icon"></span>
                        <div>
                            <a href="tel:+254704813110">+254 704 813110</a>
